Class DynamicCell<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpl.ammos.mpsa.aerie.merlinsdk.utilities.DynamicCell<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Supplier<T>
    public final class DynamicCell<T>
extends Object
implements Supplier<T>
    A dynamically-scoped cell. For best effect, store an instance of this field in a `private static final` class variable, and allow access only via static methods that fetch the current value of the cell.
